Hibernate:

  - maps the java object into table entity column.

Install Hibernate:
  -  download the hiberate jar and extract.
  -  inside lib folder, required & jpa are the two important folder.
  -  import hibernate.jar & jars present in the required and jpa folder.

Steps:
   - hibernate jdbc database config - achieve using hibernate config
   - model object - achieve through annotations
   - service method to create the model object - use to hiberate api.
   - database design - not needed.
   - dao method save object using sql queries - not needed.
